{"tid":393584,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【箍牙FD子入】邊條ON9發明固定器？","createTime":"2017-09-09T11:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T05:44:10.000Z","uid":9767,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5450cc6e1de75e6fc88bd3b887f1c0aaee459b","tid":393584,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"係咪以為自己好撚醒好撚有創意？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫完春入返正題 宜家個固定器搞到變左痴利根 下排嗰舊無乜點 但上排牙嗰舊膠完全阻撚住發音 仲要頂撚住條脷 吞口水都變到麻撚煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n醫生話會習慣 佢意思係習慣之後會慢慢變返正常 定會習慣痴利根呀我屌你老味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf7dcfa3e71ccebb9957381e611983f7c6a56d4","tid":393584,"uid":16120,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚戴囉"},{"pid":"5de13620db1d97277bb4dfa1311a0d8da493447c","tid":393584,"uid":48016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"慢慢變成固定器既形狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca6ce5a52523f4fd91b603e1a78213a0b9876fc","tid":393584,"uid":141387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪以為自己好撚醒好撚有創意？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫完春入返正題 宜家個固定器搞到變左痴利根 下排嗰舊無乜點 但上排牙嗰舊膠完全阻撚住發音 仲要頂撚住條脷 吞口水都變到麻撚煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n醫生話會習慣 佢意思係習慣之後會慢慢變返正常 定會習慣痴利根呀我屌你老味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會變返正常呀<br />\n不過固定器真係好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但冇佢 箍噤耐前功盡費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adde22ff8ee6768e7b4f4c46bf132a54691ccf13","tid":393584,"uid":97360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開頭忍耐下<br />\n半年左右可以開始唔洗24小時戴，訓覺戴就得"},{"pid":"bb01f003aa78275e17a7245711c360c4b32284be","tid":393584,"uid":11243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"好明白樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年第一日戴固定器返學痴脷根 比人笑到傻左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以頭半年我通常都係一返到屋企先戴 但都無走到位<br />\n之後就可以訓覺先戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家反而係訓覺唔戴會唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好前功盡廢呀"},{"pid":"662256f76bac764bdfed928bb2db08185baa4f9c","tid":393584,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:58:37.000Z","msg":"想問吓 下排牙嘅固定器用條脷就可以頂到佢甩係咪正常？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上排牙嘅固定器就好實 用條脷頂唔甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df04800349d9ea2a10dd26efb1cb24d41c0e2a1","tid":393584,"uid":128198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"唔可以整全透明牙套個隻固定器咩？（貴d）"},{"pid":"a054b225c4e0cba94d01d1b787d848edfcd4b6ad","tid":393584,"uid":72943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:14:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩箍左半個月報到"},{"pid":"49329f0b21f8619a472ee7d09fd49cfc681abd18","tid":393584,"uid":96303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問吓 下排牙嘅固定器用條脷就可以頂到佢甩係咪正常？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上排牙嘅固定器就好實 用條脷頂唔甩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔正常 可能第一次戴怕你痛較鬆啲<br />\n去同醫生講啦<br />\n仲有2個星期內講野會變番正常"},{"pid":"a388d2077da6f8f99a60ebc0954055756bf28519","tid":393584,"uid":128198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以整全透明牙套個隻固定器咩？（貴d）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/023337_79dc5439e19bb59c8289c64070ce609b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F023337_79dc5439e19bb59c8289c64070ce609b.jpg&h=c6ab093b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/023338_2de8632ad16031d78df462ee77fb4bd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F023338_2de8632ad16031d78df462ee77fb4bd6.jpg&h=0b3ae586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c8da176591aca3b691410ae22d9e24f4cd47207","tid":393584,"uid":36993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:56:13.000Z","msg":"invisalign 已經前功盡廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔見咗倒模嘅retainer,得返個鋼線<br />\n完全hold 唔返啲位"},{"pid":"ee47e92fef00b0ea990638a31db8f827ea642720","tid":393584,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔可以整全透明牙套個隻固定器咩？（貴d）</blockquote><br />\n個醫生完全無提過 無啦啦拎出黎叫我戴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c91c351ddc18265c01bce83787becae430b641","tid":393584,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:30:08.000Z","msg":"太麻煩要帶24小時<br />\n放棄咗 走緊位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75e69482abf01a89cf7aa9ea787a6b332fd815c","tid":393584,"uid":22901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"之前箍嗰陣兩邊大牙經常咬到面頰 痛到飯都唔想食<br />\n完工之後索性唔戴固定<br />\n<br />\n過咗4年係走咗少少位 但咬合正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6ecdfc307ec9c25021eb2c870c01ab0caf570b","tid":393584,"uid":128198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔可以整全透明牙套個隻固定器咩？（貴d）</blockquote><br />\n個醫生完全無提過 無啦啦拎出黎叫我戴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢款固定器成本比較高，一套都要3-4K+"}]}